    XSDAll, XSDAnnotation, XSDAny, XSDAppinfo, XSDAttribute, XSDAttributeGroup, XSDBasedXMLNode, XSDChoice, XSDComplexContent, XSDComplexType, XSDDocumentation, XSDElement, XSDElementContainer, XSDEnumeration, XSDExtension, XSDGroup, XSDImport, XSDImportOrInclude, XSDInclude, XSDMaxLength, XSDMinLength, XSDPattern, XSDRestriction, XSDSchema, XSDSequence, XSDSimpleContent, XSDSimpleType, XSDTotalDigits, XSDTypeBase, XSDUnion, XSDXMLNode

    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

As such the list returned from this method should be considered immutable.
